<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="firmly-adv">firmly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fɜːmli/    美 /'fɜːrmli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>坚定地；牢牢地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>"I can manage,"she said firmly.
“我应付得了。”她坚定地说。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The woman held her daughter firmly in her arms.
这个女人把女儿紧紧地搂在怀里。</p></div></div>